text.tspan: Eating disorders prevalence, males vs. females, 2021
Estimated share of people who had eating disorders (only includes anorexia nervosa and bulimia nervosa) in the
past year, whether or not they were diagnosed, based on representative surveys, medical data and statistical
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2024); HYDE (2023); Gapminder (2022); UN WPP (2024)
Note: To allow for comparisons between countries and over time, this metric is age-standardized.
